         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... without fear, ready, ... started (?) to go ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... four heads [and] eight eyes. The elephant ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... these two ornaments are seen on him. ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... acting ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... yet I still live now. 1. || ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... thought ... an instant such ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... terrible ... being ... she me ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b5"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... be ready to receive it! 1. ||</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
         <div type="comments">
            <p><note type="remarks">According to <bibl><title corresp="ref:broomhead1962"/><citedRange>291</citedRange></bibl> "[w]ritten in medium ductus the writing is very clear. The middle of a five line manuscript."</note></p>
